  <name>Valkey Insight</name>
  <summary>A Valkey insight application built with Rust and egui</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Valkey Insight is a modern database management and monitoring tool for Valkey servers.
      Built with Rust and the egui framework, it provides a fast and responsive user interface for
      managing your Valkey instances.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Connect to Valkey servers</li>
      <li>Monitor server performance and statistics</li>
      <li>Browse and manage keys</li>
      <li>Execute commands and queries</li>
      <li>View detailed insight about your database</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
